data.text:
SHIPPING INFORMATION

Our products are shipped all over the world. We use both air and sea freight. The companies we work with are:

Certain countries in the world are eligible for our free shipping program. If your shipping destination falls under any of the following regions, we will ship your purchase to you free of charge. Please see here for eligible countries.

Note: The customer has to pay the additional taxes (VAT/GST) and duties (to customs) when clearing the merchandise from customs according to the norms of their respective countries. These taxes and duties in most cases are very nominal and are exempt in some countries.
